am/apps/2362630/extras/c82149dfedb83ddedf2b785dc185f8fd.mp4?t=1758156937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >19 Unique Bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each boss having their own set of attacks and themes. All except the Elite Generals being randomly selected for each level. Designed to be a challenge for every mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362630/extras/8972039dd7c057ba71903ad6e9bbd1dc.poster.avif?t=1758156937\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362630/extras/8972039dd7c057ba71903ad6e9bbd1dc.webm?t=1758156937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2362630/extras/8972039dd7c057ba71903ad6e9bbd1dc.mp4?t=1758156937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you defeat every Elite General?</p>",
